Output docs/gifs/run.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1280
Set Height 720
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Set Padding 20

Hide
Type "cd ~/developer/ai/playground/claude-routines"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "claude"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "run trig_018DCw7cufB9naM71eRoFYVi"
Sleep 200ms
Enter
Sleep 25s

Ctrl+D
Sleep 1s
